      "content": "i get the logic, but it seems kind of problematic though. how can they claim it's \"objective\" when historians often disagree on what the original meaning actually was? it feels like they can just pick and choose whatever historical fact fits the outcome they want. isn't that just a way to give legal legitimacy to specific political outcomes?",
